{"id": "a2f24c26e139b270023556019c479946cc1c7e9531a14a3850c8246bb44d4473", "item_id": "9b214c614f:0", "text": "MaterialX Lama is a state of the art material layering system developed at Industrial Light & Magic that introduces a modular approach to building material networks and includes recent shading R&D work on energy conservation and dispersion."}
{"id": "19c9732eb63eaa48cd74de49ae4386efd2a60d8dac5b3c808654ab56a66ea6e2", "item_id": "9b214c614f:1", "text": "The MaterialX Lama project represents ongoing R&D into materials at ILM, and represents one facet of the larger MaterialX project."}
{"id": "d74263299aa65432109bd465a2e16b8a97bc4a7e0f6c6af0144076566c06635b", "item_id": "9b214c614f:2", "text": "MaterialX Lama node composition also offers a simpler built-in mechanism for energy conservation and other properties, because of its fundamental focus on layering of physically based responses."}
{"id": "b5112c924dbccf509793a0746c85d3bea86639c8a8816b1c08da14cbac3fcd18", "item_id": "9b214c614f:3", "text": "MaterialX Lama is battle-tested at ILM and RenderMan will be able to take advantage of ongoing work as it evolves."}
